# The shipped skill dir must contain ONLY the three packaged files (SKILL.md, LICENSE, and
# skill-resources.zip). Running the SessionStart extractor against this SOURCE tree - which happens
# during local testing or when a duck/agent runs the hook here - unpacks the zip in place, leaving
# tools/, references/, dist/, vendor/, and a .skill-resources-<version>.ok marker behind. Ignore
# every such extraction artifact so a polluted tree can never be accidentally staged or committed
# (test_shipped_skill_dir_is_minimal is the CI backstop; this keeps it from ever getting that far).
pkg/skills/commentable-html/*
!pkg/skills/commentable-html/SKILL.md
!pkg/skills/commentable-html/LICENSE
!pkg/skills/commentable-html/skill-resources.zip
